        <em>Vampire: The Masquerade</em>, <em>World of Darkness</em>, and related marks are trademarks of Paradox Interactive AB. This is an unofficial fan project and is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or sponsored by Paradox Interactive or White Wolf Entertainment.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
</shared.PageLayout>
